<ContentLayout
  title="SE Ranking Website Audit: Affordable Alternative Reviewed"
  description="SE Ranking offers a solid website audit tool at a fraction of the cost of Ahrefs or Semrush. See what it checks, how it scores sites, and whether it's right for you."
